;05Aug2003 KK  Derived this file from update.lst and edited to
;          contain the copy specifications for bootburn.o and bootrom.hex
;          needed for use by "msupdate.exe  ip_address  bootburn".
;          NOTE: Must remove /flash/MSSC.O at least prior to doing the
;                preceding so there is enough space in /flash/ to receive
;                the large bootrom.hex file.
;09Mar2010 KK  Added SC3type column to this file format for use with 
;          msupdate version 3.96 adding support for Smartcard3.2 .
;
;SC3type    PC File Name        SC3 File Name                  Comments
SC3         bootburn.o          /flash/bootburn.o              ;1.2/22T
SC3         bootrom.hex         /flash/bootrom.hex             ;1.2/22T
SC3Plus     bootburn.o          /flash/bootburn.o              ;1.2/22T
SC3Plus     bootrom.hex         /flash/bootrom.hex             ;1.2/22T
SC3p2       bootburn.o.SC3p2    /flash/bootburn.o              ;1.2/26T
SC3p2       bootrom.hex.SC3p2   /flash/bootrom.hex             ;1.2/26T
